snippet.title: Smash Ultimate Opening but the lyrics are what's happening onscreen
snippet.description:
I wonder how many more characters I could have unlocked in the time it took me to make this literal… XD Also, Girlfriend Reviews did a literal parody of this song before me (I missed it because it's labeled as another video) and it's hilarious! Not that she really needs endorsement from a scrub like me lol, but check it out (starts at about the 4 minute mark, but those first 4 minutes are gold so you should watch them too: https://youtu.be/HJeiKhF04Uc)

*takes shovel*
*digs I'M REALLY FEELING IT meme out of the Sm4sh grave*
I'M REALLY FEELING IIIIIIIIT

Credit to cristhian oliveira for this amazing instrumental of Lifelight!
